    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly project or daily-with-character. Engine starts, runs, and pulls with good torque, transmission engages, and the chassis feels like a workable foundation for someone who knows their way around maintenance. Not a show car, but it has honest mechanical potential, useful parts value, and plenty of life left for the right owner. Great candidate for a fixer-upper, commuter backup, or platform to sort and improve over time.",
